commitResults.messageBody:
Changes:
1) Merge add-related TaskLogic code toTaskList, as the role of TaskList is to manage all task related functions
2) Reduce classes for adding to one, i.e. only AddCommand remains
3) Identifier is change to type Integer to accept null values, so that it will accept null if it is not a repeating task
4) Edit methods to parse user input for the add feature. Allow TaskParser to parse and attempt a try catch for exceptions thrown.
With Parser being broken down into sub parsers, the job of TaskParser is now to break down user input into smaller subsections and analyse
and convert these smaller inputs into a suitable type or attribute that Task class can accept
5) Add feature for sorting task and accepting only tasks whose timings do not clash with the
existing task in the taskList. User is assumed to be assisted with this feature to plan his/her time properly and focus
on one task during an allocated time period.
